item.title: CVE-2019-19277|2024-08-05T02:09:39.511Z -- siemens%20ag -- siport%20mp
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in SIPORT MP (All versions < 3.1.4). Vulnerable versions of the device allow the creation of special accounts ("service users") with administrative privileges that could enable a remote authenticated attacker to perform actions that are not visible to other users of the system, such as granting persons access to a secured area.
